      "text": "Iterator Design Pattern:- Same as our DSA wala iterators simple - Design Problem hai like\nDesign your own iterator!!!\n\n",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Iterator Design Pattern:- Same as our DSA wala iterators simple - Design Problem hai like\nDesign your own iterator!!!\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "M_1hil7RiNEFfL7AVKGQ8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 99.26050204918033,
      "y": 294.7986680327869,
      "width": 1417.6190185546875,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
